Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:14.41,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}找不到合适的话语　轻抚你的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:21.04,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你一言不发　冷冷挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:27.58,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}小小的误解　令年轻的爱瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:34.68,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不想见你悲伤的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:41.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即便抛弃梦想　请别抛弃你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:47.69,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}让它永远在我心中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.63,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}有一天　不同的你我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}携手筑起未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:02.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}回到曾经的地方　不论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:09.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}现在二人只有悲伤地错开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:14.60,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相信后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:30.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}不堪回首　互相争斗的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:38.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}轻抚脸颊　微微一笑释之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:46.67,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}驻足于此　不见星之歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:56.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}奏出名为爱的幻曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:04.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}心与心远离　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:16.17,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}天边卷云翻滚　眺望同一缕光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIA…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经…被我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人了！他已经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈乌梅亚的守护石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不让人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知我杀了基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:31.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}约定的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.35,0:02:31.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XR-a 奥美嘉3频道导航系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始入港程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入港管制塔来电
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥美嘉3导航系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始入港程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认信号后转为自动驾驶 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认导航信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海计算机同步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换为自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真给他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈尔巴顿的怨念在保护他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 保护他们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么直白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨瑟兰上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 最后关头强袭和驾驶员的MIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是万幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GAT系列今后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将成为我们的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人知道是调整人孩子在驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成何体统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像被人当面否定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我们赢不了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有技术已经得到继承并发展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要为我们所用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟阿兹拉尔怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有问题由我们进行修正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场可悲的意外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:29.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an2\pos(640,610)\fs60}独眼巨人系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括 即将发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切为了蓝色纯净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统合作战室 通知第八舰队所属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军事司令部 威廉·萨瑟兰上校注
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犒劳各位长期以来的艰苦作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为准备听证会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰在接到命令前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持现状 继续舰内待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 「维持现状」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拿马局势紧张 这里也很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特军 卡本塔里亚基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让人担心 想法古怪 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喜欢哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很善良 是个好人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克鲁泽 进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 报告我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该更早采取措施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲虽然不小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也在所难免
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明他确实是个强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路过程艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 尼科尔 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔菲鲁特队长 莫拉希姆队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多士兵被他夺去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成功击杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本土也获得了极高评价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将颁给你星云勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管舍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从今天起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已是国防委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直属特务部队的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是王牌机师了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将有资格驾驶最新锐机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为交接机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽早返回本土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令父当选议长的事 听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉议长从心底盼望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争早日结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想尽早结束它吗 这样的战争 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中 需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认得我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫我拉克丝吧 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 很高兴你还记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他醒了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马鲁奇奥导师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没想到吧 自己躺在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求把床放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里环境多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我做祷告的屋外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把你带到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是拥有S.E.E.D.之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿斯兰战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该死了…才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 把他的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也对阿斯兰动了杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而阿斯兰也对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这无法避免吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在和敌人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 你的敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔巴尼的让步案什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骤雨作战已经通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算全盘接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发动战役 肯定会有牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以避免 为什么不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不可理喻的议和条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人如何接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经在以胜利者自居了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样样针锋相对 不可能有实现和谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候发来这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是低劣的拖延手段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔巴尼也没有获得理事国中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有成员的同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的坐下来谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们今后放弃一切对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用枪杆进行外交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的理念吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵前议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这话过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须考虑全局意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请避免个人情绪化的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您带来的宝贵意见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最终将由我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现任最高议会讨论并作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请代我谢过马鲁奇奥导师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦他作为使者专程前来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会转告的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿各位作出着眼未来的明智决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯加的工事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说可抵御核打击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 现在用不了核武
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特也没那种打算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要实施打击 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须进入被称为大坑的内部空间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝非易事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之那不是一块好啃的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯加的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要及时进行更新
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次侦查 是特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要完全保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讲冒险故事也给我留到战后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报往往是不经意间泄露的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:29.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an2\pos(640,560)\fs60}地球军阿拉斯加最高司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统合作战室 请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第八舰队所属 大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求指示本舰下一步行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对贵舰的指示由萨瑟兰上校全权负责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请接通上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校正在会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法替你接通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰还载有扎夫特军驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这件事至今没有得到指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对贵舰的指示依然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持现状 舰内待机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能说更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅 多多少少吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能睡好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说什么时候才批准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上岸许可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在总部基地里 连着5天不准下船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 也没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩一架空中霸王了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把回收的暴风也修了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修敌机干啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那原来是我们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 估计也就调整人能驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急的话 等会再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面等着 找医生开点药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡一觉 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 医生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔也不在了 基拉也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都难过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…难过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没心情 安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 找其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实对基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜欢基拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管刚开始是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他确实人不错 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很可怕？很稀罕？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捆得牢牢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你又在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种家伙怎么会在军舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么害怕的话 当什么兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是说又傻又不中用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人男朋友死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 这婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 米丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 多尔都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙却活得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 多尔他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该都死光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天将针对第八舰队大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止的军务进行听证
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈少校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔·巴基露露中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晨07:00准时出席
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为生存 为守护 为开创
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路忘我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满身创痍回首望去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遭到冷冷指责的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当无处发泄的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指向具体的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中萌生的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「暗潮涌动」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向什么释放这愤怒 高达

